programmes said that it had been a year of change. Following board changes
and a review of operations Stylus Television and some operating units were
closed, provisions for which have been included in the accounts.
Turnover fell from Pounds 15.8m to Pounds 14.2m and the pre-tax figure was
struck after an exceptional charge of Pounds 708,000 relating to closure
